{"type":"message","id":"7167eb25","parentId":"9d02f140","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:55:14.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Context usage is at 19%, well below the 60% threshold. Nothing to alert on. HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":"f7615fdf1d0f427642c3e5e474e683380cc8a0a746da6831f06738cb9914e23e"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n📊 **Context Monitor Check — 07:55**\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 当前用量 | 19% (38,955 / 200,000 tokens) |\n| 状态 | ✅ 正常 |\n\n无需操作。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1354,"output":90,"cacheRead":37099,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38543,"cost":{"input":0.0005416,"output":0.000135,"cacheRead":0.00148396,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00216056}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773964511911}}
